English: Start 2 emergency power supply unit(s), using the command <color=orange>EMERGENCY_POWER_SUPPLY_ON</color> from terminal(s) in <color=orange>ZONE 183.</color>
Description: A text string that appears on screen when the player attempts to open a door which is locked due to an emergency lockdown. Don't alter the RichText tags.

French.Translation: Démarrez 2 unité(s) d'alimentation de secours en utilisant la commande <color=orange>EMERGENCY_POWER_SUPPLY_ON</color> depuis le ou les terminaux dans la <color=orange>ZONE 183.</color>

Italian.Translation: Avvia 2 alimentatori di emergenza usando il comando <color=orange>EMERGENCY_POWER_SUPPLY_ON</color> dai terminali nella <color=orange>ZONE 183.</color>

German.Translation: Starten Sie 2 Notstromversorgungseinheit(en) am/an den Terminal(s) in <color=orange>ZONE 183</color> mit dem Befehl <color=orange>EMERGENCY_POWER_SUPPLY_ON</color>.

Spanish.Translation: Arranca 2 unidad(es) eléctrica(s) de apoyo usando el comando <color=orange>EMERGENCY_POWER_SUPPLY_ON</color> en la(s) terminal(es) de la <color=orange>ZONE 183.</color>

Russian.Translation: Запустите 2 аварийных источника питания с помощью команды <color=orange>EMERGENCY_POWER_SUPPLY_ON</color> на терминалах в <color=orange>ZONE 183</color>.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: Inicie 2 unidade(s) de fornecimento elétrico de emergência, usando o comando <color=orange>EMERGENCY_POWER_SUPPLY_ON</color> do(s) terminal(is) na <color=orange>ZONE 183.</color>

Polish.Translation: Uruchom 2 zasilacze awaryjne za pomocą polecenia <color=orange>ERGENCY_POWER_SUPPLY_ON</color> z terminalu w <color=orange>STREFIE 183.</color>

Japanese.Translation: コマンド<color=orange>EMERGENCY_POWER_SUPPLY_ON</color>を<color=orange>ZONE 183</color>の端末に使用し、非常電力供給ユニットを2tう起動しろ。

Korean.Translation: <color=orange>ZONE 183</color> 터미널에서 <color=orange>EMERGENCY_POWER_SUPPLY_ON</color> 명령을 사용해 비상 파워 서플라이 유닛 2개 가동.

Chinese_Traditional.Translation: <color=orange>ZONE 183</color>的終端指令<color=orange>EMERGENCY_POWER_SUPPLY_ON</color>啟動2個緊急電源裝置。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: 在<color=orange>ZONE 183</color>的终端上使用命令<color=orange>EMERGENCY_POWER_SUPPLY_ON</color>启动2个应急电源装置。
